<channel|># 從頭再嚟
(pos:動詞短語)
<explanation>
yue:由最開始嘅地方重新開始做過。
eng:to start over; to start from scratch
<eg>
yue:呢份報告寫得唔太好，我諗我要從頭再嚟。 (ni1 fan6 bou3 gou3 se2 dak1 m4 tai3 hou2, ngo5 nam2 ngo5 jiu3 cung4 tau4 zoi3 lai4.)
eng:This report isn't written very well; I think I need to start over from scratch. [end of text]


